  <name>patSysinfo</name>
  <summary>Get realtime information  system information.</summary>
  <description>With patSysinfo you get a lot of data with only a few PHP-statements. 
Et voila, you get a lot of data your code can deal with it. 
If you are as lazy as me, and you do not want to write PHP-code at all, just add a patSysinfo XML element to get all needed data.</description>
